data.description: 2710 SQ FT on ONE LEVEL!!! 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms one with jacuzzi bath tub. Separate dining room, with crown molding, Built in's every where storage, storage and more storage. Also a sitting or breakfast room off of kitchen.  LOOK at the size of the family room 31'9x14'1, put your pool table in there ...Fenced back yard for the puppy's.  and an extra sun room . Partial basement has no windows but it is heated. 2 car attached garage plenty of RV parking.   All the old timers here love the Circle Drive area.  Exclude antique stove in the living room.
